text: The Spider Woman Strikes Back is a 1946 American horror movie directed by Arthur Lubin and starring Gale Sondergaard, Brenda Joyce, Kirby Grant, Milburn Stone, Rondo Hatton, Hobart Cavanaugh, Norman Leavitt. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1946 movies Category:1940s horror movies Category:American horror movies Category:Movies directed by Arthur Lubin
